# Shopping Web Application

## Overview
A full-stack e-commerce web application with multiple user roles (Admin, Vendor, Customer).

## Features
- User Authentication (Admin, Vendor, Customer)
- Product Management
- Cart System
- Dashboard Views

## Tech Stack
- Python (Flask)
- MySQL
- HTML, CSS, JavaScript

## How to Run
1. Install dependencies: pip install flask pymysql
2. Setup MySQL database
3. Run: python app.py
